WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.733 --> 00:00:04.700
Xiaojie

2
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:07.066
Xiaojie

3
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:12.633
Sister Meng

4
00:00:13.333 --> 00:00:14.766
Even if you divorce me

5
00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:16.966
I will definitely prove to you

6
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:19.066
Shen Guiying is your biological mother

7
00:00:25.066 --> 00:00:26.900
Daughter, are you alright?

8
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.400
Mom, I'm sorry.

9
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:35.466
It's my daughter's fault

10
00:00:35.466 --> 00:00:36.600
Wronged you

11
00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:39.966
Don't worry, I will never doubt you in the future.

12
00:00:39.966 --> 00:00:42.233
I won't let you suffer any grievances.

13
00:00:44.166 --> 00:00:47.900
Now I am the legitimate old lady of the Zhang family

14
00:00:48.066 --> 00:00:49.900
As long as you kill Shen Guiying

15
00:00:49.966 --> 00:00:53.100
No one cares about my good deeds anymore

16
00:00:59.066 --> 00:01:02.300
Damn dumb, don't waste your time

17
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.566
I'll tell you what.

18
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:05.466
This warehouse

19
00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.500
Abandoned

20
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:09.300
Except for the old lady

21
00:01:09.566 --> 00:01:12.066
No one even knows you're here

22
00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:14.833
What do you want?

23
00:01:15.366 --> 00:01:17.066
Just know to gesticulate

24
00:01:18.266 --> 00:01:20.566
Why is your life so hard?

25
00:01:21.866 --> 00:01:23.600
Look at the wound on your face

26
00:01:23.666 --> 00:01:26.000
I was beaten like this by the old lady

27
00:01:26.366 --> 00:01:29.000
It's all buried in the ground, why are you still okay?

28
00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:32.066
How dare you come back and frame the old lady?

29
00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:34.566
It almost killed a few of us

30
00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:36.600
I'll tell you what.

31
00:01:36.766 --> 00:01:39.833
Today we will teach me a good lesson

